=== Deep analysis of k=4 case (p_k=7, p_{k+1}=11) ===
Prime powers in (7, 10]: 8=2^3, 9=3^2
lcm contribution of 8: factor of 2 (since 4=2^2 already in lcm(1..7))
lcm contribution of 9: factor of 3 (since 3=3^1 already in lcm(1..7))
Total ratio = 2*3 = 6
p_k = 7
Margin in log: log(7) - log(6) = 0.154151

